  "source": "// Design example: deterministic map iteration with bounds\n// Note: multi-entry iteration requires a state map.\n\nseiyaku MapDemo {\n  state Entries: Map<int, int>;\n\n  kotoage fn sum_first_two() -> int {\n    let s = 0;\n    for (k, v) in Entries.take(2) {\n      s = s + v;\n    }\n    return s;\n  }\n}\n",
